title: Bob & Tom - Motorheads
description:
My darling-oldest-daughter, Carrie, gave me these tapes when she was a student at IU - Bloomington, and I love her dearly for them. She has the same perverted sense-of-humour as me!

I always thought that they were funny-as-hell, and the &#039;suicide-attempt&#039;, about #10, is the one of the funniest things I&#039;ve ever heard!

Thanks, Carrie ... Love, Dad ... aka &#039;gonzo5440&#039; on TPB Forum ...
